<plot>Professor Logan (Leo G. Carroll) is involved in an adult panel discussion of five sex-related issues dramatized in five separate but integrated sequences: "Honeymoon" (pre-marital relations), "Homecoming'(extra-marital relations), "The Divorcee" (promiscuity among divorcees), "Average Man" (problems of the average man in sexual relations) and "Baby" (a story of abortion).</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?412563</url></doc>
